        <div class="feature__content">
          <h3 class="feature__heading">Hey Ram(History, Drama)</h3>
          <p>
            "Hey Ram" is a powerful and thought-provoking Indian historical drama directed by Kamal Haasan, who also stars in the lead role. The film intertwines personal and political narratives, set against the backdrop of India's tumultuous partition and the assassination of Mahatma Gandhi. It follows the journey of Saket Ram, a man initially driven by revenge for his wife's death during the communal riots, but whose life takes a transformative turn as he confronts his own beliefs and the broader socio-political landscape. With its rich storytelling, stellar performances, and deep exploration of themes like violence, redemption, and historical memory, "Hey Ram" offers a profound and immersive cinematic experience. The filmâ€™s intricate portrayal of historical events and personal transformation makes it a compelling watch, leaving a lasting impact on its audience.
          </p>
          <a href="https://www.imdb.com/title/tt0108052/?ref_=nv_sr_srsg_0" class="link-arrow">Learn More</a>
        </div>
