      <article class="grid grid--1x2 feature">
        <div class="feature__content">
       
          <h3 class="feature__heading">Sarpatta Parambarai</h3>
          <p>
        
            "Sarpatta Parambarai" is an exhilarating Tamil sports drama directed by Pa. Ranjith, featuring Arya in the lead role. Set in the 1970s, the film explores the intense rivalry between two boxing clans in North Chennai, focusing on Kabilan, an underdog boxer from the Sarpatta clan. As Kabilan strives to prove his worth in the boxing ring, he battles personal demons, societal expectations, and the shadows of his family's past. With its gripping narrative, dynamic boxing sequences, and rich cultural backdrop, "Sarpatta Parambarai" vividly portrays the spirit of resilience and the quest for redemption. The film's detailed depiction of the era, coupled with powerful performances and an emotional storyline, makes it an inspiring and unforgettable cinematic experience. The raw portrayal of the struggles and triumphs within the boxing community highlights the deep-rooted cultural and social dynamics of the time, making "Sarpatta Parambarai" a must-watch for its authenticity and emotional depth.
          </p>
          <a href="https://www.imdb.com/title/tt1798709/?ref_=nv_sr_srsg_0" class="link-arrow">Learn More</a>
        </div>
